### Summary

Narrative-based augmented reality puzzle game using the Google Tango as a tool to travel through time, and to see into the ghost world. There is an angry spirit in the room, turning on lights, making sounds, and setting off the Reliever contraption. 

<div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
    <iframe loop class="embed-responsive-item" src="/img/portfolio/spiritus/IMG_5357.mp4" type="video/mp4"> </iframe>
 </div>

### Support

Sam Sadtler worked on the wireless communications between the objects. This project was supported by NYU Game Innovation Lab and NYU Tisch Experiments in Storytelling.

